dmcache utilities
=================

mkdmcache
---------

Create a cache device.

Usage: mkdmcache CACHE_NAME CACHE_DISK ORIG_DEV

CACHE_NAME - a name for the device mapper cache device

CACHE_DISK - the disk device to be used as a cache

ORIG_DEV   - the device to be cached

rmdmcache
---------

Remove a cache device.

Usage: rmdmcache CACHE_NAME

CACHE_NAME - a name of an existing cache device
